<span class="label">ACM News</span>
<h2>A Softer Approach to Robotics</h2>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Samuel Greengard
<br/>
September 12, 2023<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
